Create files for theme customization

Usage:
  madness theme full [PATH]
  madness theme css
  madness theme colors
  madness config (-h|--help)

Commands:
  full
    Create a full theme customization directory in PATH [default: _theme]

  css
    Create a folder with the entire CSS file for customization

  colors
    Create a folder with CSS for overriding colors only

Options:
  -h --help
    Show this help
